        "cooked": "<p>Android 15 will have notification cool down built into the OS natively.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.androidcentral.com/apps-software/android-15-notification-cooldown\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/2/f2628bfd100f6e590a769cb585190e8a76c2295e.png\" class=\"site-icon\" data-dominant-color=\"A8C056\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.androidcentral.com/apps-software/android-15-notification-cooldown\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"07:17PM - 17 February 2024\">Android Central ‚Äì 17 Feb 24</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/388;\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/5/25ad1c6d4460b7399d6e4501fc9a96c65dc13a56_2_690x388.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"7C6D48\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.androidcentral.com/apps-software/android-15-notification-cooldown\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">New Android 15 feature will make repeated notifications less annoying</a></h3>\n\n  <p>The feature will limit the annoyance factor of notifications that come in succession.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
