        "created_at": "2024-03-02T20:56:32.377Z",
        "cooked": "<p>So if someone sends a message, you just want to get one notification that says ‚ÄúYou have unread notifications‚Äù and persists until the chat no longer has unread notifications, but otherwise doesn‚Äôt get refreshed/repeated/etc even if additional messages are sent?</p>",
